Super excited to be helping out on this project✨ 

You might remember the cautionary tale of Ebenezer Scrooge - a miserly old man visited by spirits who took through a series of flashbacks as dire warnings of how he was wasting his life by #charlesdickens #achristmascarol.
This Christmas classic has been told and retold many times. 

In our version it gets a modern update with a feminine + cultural twist with Sita, an Indian American woman, grappling with her impending life of drudgery. The spirits of 3 important female mentors visit her from her past on the 3rd night of #diwali, the Festival of Lights.
We're so excited to share this story with the world!
And you can help us by recommending brands, people and companies who would love to support female led,
BIPoC storytelling!

We're looking for introductions to:
*Desi fashion labels
*jewelers
*snack + sweet makers 

DM : @mohadohaprods @moha_doha for more information, questions, comments or just compliments✨ 

You can also help support us through our gofundme page : 

https://www.gofundme.com/f/remix-a-christmas-carol-as-a-diwali-story
